       Sets global parameters for signal electromigration. Use this command to
       specify the required verify_AC_limit mode settings before  running  any
       commands that perform signal electromigration. The parameters specified
       with  the  set_signal_em_analysis_mode  command are then used automati-
       cally whenever signal electromigration takes place.

       Use the get_signal_em_analysis_mode command to return the current  set-
       tings for the set_signal_em_analysis_mode command.

       Note:  Use  the  -method  parameter to specify the waveform calculation
       method to be used (rms, peak, or avg).

